OL,4,CChinese county bans birthday parties in
OL,5,Cbid to be frugal
OL,6, A county in southwest China has banned
OL,7, birthday parties and other
OL,8, celebrations, following calls from the
OL,9, central government to be more frugal.
OL,11,FIt also set out new rules for weddings
OL,12,Fand funerals, including a ban on cash
OL,13,Fgifts more than 200 yuan (#22, US$31).
OL,15,FThe rules in Funing county only apply
OL,16,Fto all communist party members, civil
OL,17,Fservants and village organisation
OL,18,Fleaders - not to most residents.
OL,20,FIt is a traditional Chinese custom to
OL,21,Fgive cash gifts at parties.
